{
  "name": "Blessing of Zephyr",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "icons/magic/air/wind-swirl-purple-blue.webp",
  "system": {
    "itemKey": "blessingOfZephyr",
    "description": "<p><span class=\"cf0\">You grant a creature with range a Climb Speed and Jump Distance equal to their Speed for the duration.</span></p><p><span class=\"cf0\"><strong>Spell Cast:</strong> When you cast the Spell, make a DC 15 Spell Check.</span></p><ul><li><p><span class=\"cf0\"><strong>Success:</strong> The target can immediately move in any direction (including jumping) up to their Speed.</span></p></li></ul><p><em><strong>System Tip:</strong> Any bonus speed (except of  Greater Blessing enhancement) will not be added to the Jump Distance. You need to keep track of it.</em></p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Spell Enhancements</span></strong></span></p><p><span class=\"cf0\"><strong>Range: (1 AP, Repeatable) </strong>The range of the Spell increases by 5 Spaces. You can use this Enhancement a maximum of two times.</span></p><p><strong>Duration: (1 MP, Repeatable)</strong> The duration increases by 1 step (10 min → 1 hour → 8 hours → Long Rest).</p><p><strong>Targets: (1 AP + X MP)</strong> You can target X additional creatures within range. The AP cost of this Enhancement can’t be paid for with MP (See Mana Points on AP Enhancements).</p><p><strong>Zephyr Walk: (1 MP)</strong> The target ignores Difficult Terrain for the duration.</p><p><strong>Greater Blessing: (1 MP, Repeatable)</strong> The target’s Speed increases by 2.</p>",
